<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_01_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema514_01.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_01_ih_0002">
      <section class="title flex_wrap">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <span class="recap" lang="y">이전에 <span>배웠어요</span></span>
        </h2>
        <div class="title_sub">
          <span lang="y">『수학 3-2』 분모가 같은 분수의 크기 비교</span>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">
          분수만큼 색칠하고, 두 분수의 크기를 비교하여 <span class="circle_blank"></span>&nbsp;안에 <img src="./../../common_contents/common/img/icon_arrow_right.svg" alt="크다" /><span class="ml-14"></span>, <img src="./../../common_contents/common/img/icon_equal.svg" alt="같다" /><span class="ml-14"></span>,
          <img src="./../../common_contents/common/img/icon_arrow_left.svg" alt="작다" />
          중 알맞은 것을 고르세요.
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box">
          <div class="block_group">
            <div class="item">
              <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="1">
                <button type="button">
                  <span></span>
                  <span></span>
                  <span></span>
                  <span></span>
                  <span></span>
                  <span></span>
                </button>
              </div>
              <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="1">
                <button type="button"></button>
                <button type="button"></button>
                <button type="button"></button>
                <button type="button"></button>
                <button type="button"></button>
                <button type="button"></button>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="item">
              <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="1">
                <button type="button">
                  <span></span>
                  <span></span>
                  <span></span>
                  <span></span>
                  <span></span>
                  <span></span>
                </button>
              </div>
              <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="5">
                <button type="button">
                  <span></span>
                </button>
                <button type="button"></button>
                <button type="button"></button>
                <button type="button"></button>
                <button type="button"></button>
                <button type="button"></button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="fraction_group">
            <div class="fraction_box_mixed">
              <span>1</span>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>6</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown math_symbol" data-answer-single="<">
                <option></option>
                <option value=">">></option>
                <option value="=">=</option>
                <option value="<"><</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="fraction_box_mixed">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>11</span>
                <span>6</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">분수만큼 색칠하면</p>
                <div class="flex align_center gap_20" lang="y">
                  <div class="fraction_box_mixed">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span>6</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="ml-14">보다</span>

                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>11</span>
                    <span>6</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="ml-14">이 더 많이 색칠됩니다. 따라서</span>

                  <div class="fraction_box_mixed">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span>6</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  &lt;
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>11</span>
                    <span>6</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="ml-14">입니다.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <!-- <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button> -->
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
